Usage:
Step 0: Enable "ForceStop" in "Settings" —> "Accessibility";
Step 1: Go to "Black list" from the right-top of last page;
Step 2: Click "REFRESH" every time you edit the black list;
Step 3: Click "LET'S GO" and there your are.

Test on Nexus 5X hosting Android 7.0 only.

Contribute your efforts on https://github.com/tigaliang/ForceStop and post any issues through github or liangkangabc@gmail.com.
